                                    <h2>Just No</h2>
                                    <hr class="star-light">
                                    <p>These are the shows from this year that were bad. All of these had huge storytelling problems and need to seriously reassess what's going on behind the scenes. These are in no particular order.</p>
                                </div>
                                <div id="mediocre" class="tab-pane fade">
                                    <h2>Mediocre</h2>
                                    <hr class="star-light">
                                    <p>These are the shows from this year that just weren't good enough. All of these had at least a few storytelling problems and need to consider changing things up. These are in no particular order.</p>
                                </div>
                                <div id="honMention" class="tab-pane fade">
                                    <h2>Honorable Mention</h2>
                                    <hr class="star-light">
                                    <p>These are the shows from this year that didn't make the cut. Some of these were good, but may have had too many flaws in their storytelling to justify a place on the list while others were just okay. These are in no particular order.</p>
